: 686}, {\"ngram\": \"alreadyBritain's best-ever gymnast\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"a distanceand\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the motivation\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not shy away from that stuff anymore,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that stuff\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was younger, I never used to think about medals or results and where you stand in history.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now I have learned how important it is to grab motivation from everywhere you possibly can.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"motivation\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making history is one of those and I would love to give myself the opportunity to do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In pursuit of immortality, the 30-year-old has built a fiendish routine that will have a much higher difficulty score than any of his rivals.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pursuit\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"immortality\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"a fiendish routine\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"a much higher difficulty score\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is shorter than his Tokyo routine, packed with pitfalls and difficult combinations, with a tariff so high he knows that, if he completes it, he iscertain to win a fourth Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9910310924412472, \"rank\": 0.00712067803101029, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pitfalls\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"difficult combinations\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a tariff\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"a fourth Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since I was a youngster, I have always wanted to increase my difficulty level every time I come back to a major competition,\\\" he explains.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a youngster\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"my difficulty level\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"a major competition\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have that fire in my belly, that feeling of being inspired and trying to do more.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that fire\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"my belly\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never wanted to go back to the same routine, I have always tried to increase the difficulty every single time for 24 years.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same routine\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulty\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"24 years\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All I need to do is focus on me, I do not need to compete against anyone else or worry about what they are doing.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a running race.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a running race\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do my job, and I have the potential to win titles.\\\"\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my job\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whitlock obsesses over the routine, completing it hundreds of times each week in training at South EssexGymnasticsClub.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whitlock\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the routine\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"South EssexGymnasticsClub\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the road to his fourth Olympics, rarified air in such a physically demanding sport, Whitlock has adapted his training intensity.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.780016800441532e-25, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"his fourth Olympics\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ng