ock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this relationship\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had a lot of fun filming their TV adverts and I would never have got those opportunities otherwise.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"their TV adverts\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"those opportunities\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I work with a lot of different brands, but Aldi has been one that has stood out as a lot of fun along this journey.\\\"\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3103, \"end\": 3107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"different brands\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"this journey\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During that time Whitlock's motivation has shifted dramatically, with Paris set to be the first Games where wife Leah and daughter Willow can watch him compete.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3195, \"end\": 3203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.780016800441532e-25, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 3248, \"end\": 3253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or